    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Preserved specimens, dorsal view. A, Polyonyx gibbesi Haig, 1956, male (MZUSP- 7146); B, Pisidia brasiliensis Haig in Rodrigues da Costa, 1968, male (MZUSP- 11300); C, Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820), male (MZUSP- 13727); D, Porcellana sigsbeiana A. Milne-Edwards, 1880, male (USNM- 35401). Scales: A, C – D (5 mm); B (1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261200/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

